products.name: Even Better Compact Makeup Broad Spectrum SPF 15
products.description: A light cream with a powdery finish, our compact makeup creates more even-toned skin, instantly. Shades for Very Fair, Moderately Fair, Medium, Deep.

products.name: Redness Solutions Makeup Broad Spectrum SPF 15 With Probiotic Technology
Stay-Matte Oil-Free Makeup
products.description: Tested for streaking and fading at 88°F with a constant 80% humidity, all to prove Stay-Matte stays fresh. At the same time, this patent-pending formula absorbs shine, controls oil, resists sweat. And you stay matte all day.

products.name: Repairwear Laser Focus All-Smooth Makeup Broad Spectrum SPF 15
Perfectly Real Compact Makeup
products.description: Silky, oil-free formula looks like your skin—only better. Optimizes skin's varying tones to create a more even appearance. Buildable coverage lasts for hours, yet feels like nothing at all. Controls shine. In a ready-to-go, ready-to-perfect compact. Oil-free.

products.name: Chubby in the Nude Foundation Stick
products.description: Portable perfection for full-face coverage, or bare-minimum touch-ups. Creamy, moisturizing foundation stick blends easily. Builds from sheer to moderate coverage with a natural finish. Long-wearing. Oil-free.

products.name: Super City Block™ BB Cushion Compact Broad Spectrum SPF 50
products.description: Everything skin needs to face city life—flawlessly. Buildable, breathable fluid makeup feels cool and weightless on skin, yet delivers a lasting natural-matte finish. High-level SPF and antioxidants help protect against skin-damaging UV, impurities and environmental aggressors. All in a ready-to-go compact with puff applicator.

products.name: Superpowder Double Face Makeup
products.description: Powder and foundation combined in one portable compact. Long-wearing, full-coverage powder works as an over-foundation finisher or as a powder foundation. Extra-cling formula for double coverage.

products.name: Perfectly Real Makeup
products.description: Feels like nothing at all. Yet creates your skin's most perfected, natural look. Patent-pending* micro-mirrored technology optically resurfaces skin. Ultra-lightweight liquid formula is oil-free, non-acnegenic. *US and International Patents Pending

products.name: Wear Everywhere Neutrals All About Shadow 8-Pan Palette
products.description: Versatile eye shadow palettes are perfect for day… amped up for night when you layer multiple shades for extra depth and dimension. Long-wearing shades are crease- and fade-resistant. Ophthalmologist tested, too.

products.name: Pretty Easy™ Eye Palette
products.description: Clinique's Pretty Easy Eye Palette comes with eight shades of long-wearing All About Shadow in a variety of finishes. For instant lashline definition, there's Skinny Stick, our no-sharpener-required eye liner in two must-have shades. Create your own custom eye looks or follow the illustrated how-tos.

products.name: All About Shadow Primer for Eyes
products.description: Skin-toned colour primer preps lids for improved shadow application and wear. Creates a neutral base that holds All About Shadow eye colour in place for up to 12 hours. Can be worn alone for a natural yet perfected look. Appropriate for sensitive eyes and contact lens wearers. Ophthalmologist tested.

products.name: Lid Smoothie Antioxidant 8-Hour Eye Colour
products.description: Creamy, crease-resistant eye colour wears for 8 hours. Instantly cools thanks to a unique applicator. Nourishing ingredients coax fine lid lines into a blanket of smoothness. Antioxidants help protect eye-area skin.

products.name: Touch Base For Eyes
products.description: No smearing, no fading, no creasing. Stays on until washed off. Versatile, creamy formula can be worn alone or layered under other eye shadows to give them more staying power. Acts as a holding base for powder shadow, helps it last longer. Ophthalmologist tested.

products.name: Lid Pop™
products.description: Silky, long-wearing eye shadow delivers an instant pop of colour for a virtually powderless look. Builds and blends easily to a customizable level of intensity. Appropriate for contact lens wearers and sensitive eyes.

products.name: Cream Shaper For Eyes
products.description: Creamy-smooth eyeliner pencil with a hint of shimmer. Shapes and defines with intense, stay-put colour. Non-smudging, water- and transfer-resistant. Easy to sharpen, too. Ophthalmologist tested.

products.name: Quickliner For Eyes
products.description: Automatic eyeliner pencil twists up. Glides on. Smudges to a smooth blur of colour with the convenient smudge tool on the opposite end. Needs no sharpening.

products.name: High Impact™ Custom Black Kajal
products.description: For kicked-up eye drama, go bold and black. Pigment-packed kajal pencil delivers rich, dark colour with 12 hours of staying power. Skip-proof formula resists smudging, sweat and humidity—even water. Ophthalmologist Tested. Appropriate for sensitive eyes and contact lens wearers, too.

products.name: Kohl Shaper For Eyes
products.description: Rich, satiny eyeliner glides on smoky or defined, bold or superfine. Triangular, ergonomic design provides precision control. Sharpener's built into cap. Never be caught with a dull point again. Ophthalmologist tested.

products.name: Quickliner For Eyes Intense
products.description: No need to be subtle when it's now so easy to move into the deepest, most dramatic range. Find all the intensity of a liquid liner in one simple stroke. Silky formula glides on. Stays on all day. Never needs sharpening. "Smoke" with the smudge tip on the opposite end. Ophthalmologist Tested.

products.name: Brush-On Cream Liner
products.description: Creamy eyeliner brushes on deep, smoky, eye-defining colour. Long-wearing, waterproof formula comes complete with a mini Eye Liner Brush. Ophthalmologist tested.

products.name: Soft-Pressed Powder Blusher
products.description: Warm, natural-looking powder blush for all skins. Sheer, buildable colour gives cheeks a radiant glow. Silky, fresh finish, too. Wide range of shades, from subtle to vibrant. Comes with brush applicator.

products.name: Chubby Stick Cheek Colour Balm
products.description: Creamy, mistake-proof cheek colour creates a healthy-looking glow in an instant. Oil-free.

products.name: Chubby Plump & Shine Liquid Lip Plumping Gloss
products.description: This light-reflecting, high-shine gloss enhances the appearance of lips, making them appear plump and smooth. Moisturizes, wears for hours. Feels refreshing and cool upon application. Dermatologist Tested. Allergy Tested. 100% Fragrance Free.

products.name: Quickliner For Lips
products.description: All-day lip liner. Use to line and define lips or smooth all over lips before lipstick application for extended wear. Non-drying formula helps keep lipstick in place. Prevents lipstick from feathering and bleeding. No sharpening required.

products.name: Quickliner For Lips Intense
products.description: Silky formula glides on and wears all day. Use it to define the lip line or fill in lips pre-lipstick application. Non-drying formula prevents lipstick from feathering and bleeding. No sharpening required.

products.name: Almost Lipstick
products.description: Transparent pigment merges with the unique, natural tone of your lips to create something wonderful and yours alone. Sheer, glossy. Emollient-rich and very lightweight.

products.name: Butter Shine Lipstick
products.description: The creamiest, richest, smoothest lip colour you can imagine. Our revolutionary gel formula delivers the shine of a gloss, the comfort of a lipstick. Drenches lips in moist, lush colour that glides on buttery-soft, feels luxuriously smooth.

products.name: Chubby Stick Intense Moisturizing Lip Colour Balm
products.description: Tempt lips with a soft cushion of colour that's not quite sheer, not quite opaque-just the perfect happy medium. Loaded with mango and shea butters so lips feel comfortably soft and smooth. Ten vibrant shades in all.

products.name: Long Last Soft Matte Lipstick
products.description: Long-wearing formula keeps its just-applied look for hours. Non-drying, non-feathering. Full coverage, velvety, soft matte finish.

products.name: Long Last Lipstick
products.description: Longest-wearing formula. Keeps its just-applied look for hours. Won't feather, creep, stain or dry out.

products.name: Clinique Pop Liquid™ Matte Lip Colour + Primer
products.description: Lightweight liquid lipstick covers lips with lush pigment and a modern matte finish. Wears all day. Moisturizing formula with built-in primer provides a smooth, even glide so lips feel as fresh as they look.

products.name: Chubby Stick Baby TintMoisturizing Lip Colour Balm
products.description: A bit of colour, a hefty helping of moisture. These sheers bloom on contact to bring out your lips' natural tone. The colour is different for everyone.

products.name: Clinique + Jonathan Adler: Pop Lip Colour + Primer
products.description: An exclusive collection of luminous Clinique Pop™ lipsticks by Jonathan Adler. Includes 3 limited-edition shades inspired by his favorite destinations: Palm Beach Pop, Capri Pop and Santorini Pop.  Jewel-like lipsticks in bold, saturated colors look as pretty on your lips as they do on your vanity. “The domes of Lucite are inspired by my Globo collection—glowing and glamorous. Just like Lip Pop,” says Adler.
